title: Amnaeon discography
description:
Amnaeon is "a one-man musical experience". His genre is technically metal, but he claims that "amnaeon does not have a genre. Regardless of what type of music you listen to, I highly recommend giving it a chance. You won't disappointed." Justin Bonitz does vocals, guitar, drums, and keyboard all himself. I downloaded his songs from(by reverse engineering and extracting them from the online player of course, hence the low quality). All of these files have accurate id3 tags, written by me.

If you like the music, please visit his bandcamp and buy the songs. The albums are $5 each and available in several qualities including 320kbps mp3 and FLAC. You can also find a lot of covers on soundcloudlet me know if you want me to rip that aswell.
